an Salvo]] | [[Seraph]] | [[Attacker]] | AOE/[[Blaze (XC3)|Blaze]]/Awakened+ |- | [[Viral Vector]] | [[Machine Assassin]] | [[Attacker]] | AOE/2 random debuffs |- | [[Divine Sword (XC3)|Divine Sword]] | [[Lifesage]] | [[Healer]] | Heal all on hit/Pierce |- | [[Element Genesis]] | [[Royal Summoner]] | [[Attacker]] | AOE/Elem. Discharge dmg+ |- | [[Shining Refrain]] | [[Noponic Champion]] | [[Defender (XC3)|Defender]] | Evade / Self KO↑ |- | [[Pride of Place]] | [[Lapidarist]] | [[Healer]] | Field / [[Blaze (XC3)|Blaze]] & Regen |- | [[Monado Buster]] | [[Grand Marshal]] ([[Shulk]] Only) | [[Defender (XC3)|Defender]] | AOE/Awakened+/Pierce |- | [[Infinity Blade (XC2)|Infinity Blade]] | [[Master Driver]] ([[Rex]] Only) | [[Attacker]] | AOE/Pierce/Unblockable |- | [[Infinity Blade (XC3)|Infinity Blade]] | All Classes ([[Noah]] Only) | N/A | AOE / Pierce |- | [[Unlimited Sword]] | All Classes (Noah Only) | N/A | Draw [[Lucky Seven]] |- | [[Final Lucky Seven]] | All Classes (Noah Only, after using Unlimited Sword) | N/A | AOE/Smash cmb./Pierce |- | [[Dominion Flower]] | All Classes ([[Mio]] Only) | N/A | AOE/Burst/Pierce |} {{clr}}
