=== Combos === {{main|Combo}} By linking up the controlled character with companions and connecting their Arts well, Combos can be created, allowing to [[Break (XC3)|Break]] and [[Topple (XC3)|Topple]] enemies. A Toppled enemy can be subjected to either [[Launch (XC3)|Launch]] and [[Smash (XC3)|Smash]] to deal heavy damage or [[Daze (XC3)|Daze]] and [[Burst]] to remove their Enraged buffs and provide bonus item drops.
