==== Lucky Seven Arts ==== When [[Noah]] uses his [[Unlimited Sword]] Talent Art, he gains access to unique arts that are usable for 90 seconds until Noah sheaths [[Lucky Seven]] as well as the ability to use [[Final Lucky Seven]]. Four of his arts have different effects depending on the role of Noah's current class.
