=== Fusion Arts === By fusing a Master Art with an Art of the current Class, the player can unleash one Art with the effects of both at the same time with greater power at the expense of activating both of their cooldowns at once. These arts are called '''Fusion Arts''' (Japanese: {{lang|ja|融合アーツ}}, ''Yūgō ātsu''). By using various Classes for a longer period of time, the amount of attacks one can use this way will be expanded. Fusion Arts will increase the Interlink level if used frequently, enhancing the power of the Ouroboros form.
