=== Ouroboros Power === The Ouroboros Power consist of attacks more powerful than normal Arts. They are similar to Master Arts in the base game, but cannot be transferred to other classes, each class has a unique set of Ouroboros powers. Like Master Arts in the base game, they can be fused with other arts, but various additional effects apply that depend on the combination of Ouroboros Power and Arts.
=== Fusion Arts === Fusion Arts combine the effects of the regular Art and the corresponding Ouroboros power. For each possible pairing, there is a unique Fusion Art with additional effects.
